      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! The interior is super clean, and it honestly drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it over the years, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
