    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example utilizes a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT) with Drivelogic, delivering torque to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The suspension architecture includes Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable compression and rebound stages. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, this vehicle has received preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, maintaining tight tolerances within the VANOS variable valve timing system. The hydraulic steering rack provides superior tactile feedback, complemented by a rigid subframe and a precision-aligned multi-link rear suspension setup.",
